caller_intent: Confirm whether a vehicle addition to a policy was completed, as the caller had previously received a voicemail about the matter.
resolution_steps: Heather greeted Christina and mentioned she had received a voicemail.
Asked if the vehicle addition from the quoted policy needed to be processed.
Christina confirmed the vehicle was already added.
Heather verified this by pulling up the policy in her system.
Confirmed with Christina that the ID and documentation were already in place.
Ended the call with mutual thanks and well-wishes.
summary: Heather from Alliance Insurance confirmed with Christina that a vehicle addition to her policy had already been completed, verified this through the policy system, and concluded the call with a confirmation and thanks. The interaction was brief but focused on resolving a specific administrative task.
